  <front>
    <title>DELEG Extensions for Secure Transports</title>
    <seriesInfo name="Internet-Draft" value="draft-hoffman-deleg-secure-transports-00"/>
    <author initials="P. E." surname="Hoffman" fullname="Paul E. Hoffman">
      <organization>ICANN</organization>
    </author>
    <author initials="R." surname="Weber" fullname="Ralf Weber">
      <organization>Akamai Technologies</organization>
    </author>
    <date day="26" month="May" year="2026"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>The DELEG base protocol allows a DNS zone operator to specify servers
   to be used when delegating zones to other DNS nameservers.  This
   document extends the base protocol to allow zone operators to specify
   secure transports for those delegations.</t>
    </abstract>
  </front>
